  ============================================================================
  SECTION 21 COMPLIANCE CHECKLIST - PRE-SERVICE CHECKS
  Housing Act 1988, Housing Act 2004
  ============================================================================
  Dedicated Section 21 compliance checklist for Notice Only pack.
  Maps directly to Section 21 wizard answers for accurate status display.
